# Development Workflow

## Current Sprint: Phase 1 Critical Bugs
- **YRH-1**: Video Filtering System (13 pts) 
- **YRH-2**: Cache System Debugging (8 pts)
- **YRH-3**: State Management Issues (8 pts)

## Git Workflow
```bash
# Branch naming: feature/YRH-{number}-{description}
git checkout -b feature/YRH-1-video-filtering-system

# Commit format: YRH-{number}: type(scope): description
git commit -m "YRH-1: fix(filtering): implement AND/OR logic for keywords"

# Always reference Jira issue in commits
```

## Development Process
1. **Start**: Move Jira issue to "In Progress"
2. **Code**: Create feature branch, implement, test locally
3. **Review**: Create PR, move issue to "Code Review"
4. **Deploy**: Merge PR, move to "Testing", verify, mark "Done"

## Testing Checklist
- [ ] Core functionality works in both Demo and Live modes
- [ ] Windows XP theme consistency maintained
- [ ] Mobile responsive design verified
- [ ] No console errors
- [ ] API integration functional

